TestCase: Verify that if user provide a Valid Account GroupID in the URL and if Goal is not associated to that Budget while created with both categotyData and CategoryTypeData then, in the response show the Budget Details for the provided account GroupID. Make sure that include=goal is also passed in the url - - GET /v1/budgets?groupId=12345&include=categoryTypeData,categoryData,goal

Verify that if user provide the Valid Account GroupID in the URL, user must be shown with BudgetByCategory data associated to the Account GroupID if user has created a Budget with BudgetSummary and Goal ID is not associated to it. GET /v1/budgets?groupId=12345&include=categoryData,goal

Verify that if user provide the Valid Account GroupID in the URL, user must be shown with BudgetSummary data associated to the Account GroupID if user has created a Budget with BudgetSummary and Goal ID is not associated to it. GET /v1/budgets?groupId=12345&include=categoryTypeData,goal
ExpectedErrorMsg: include goal cannot be requested for all groupIds
